>> Right after seeing this tweet, he got to work.

5
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:19,439
He built a prototype in a weekend and got his first paying customers almost immediately.

6
00:00:19,439 --> 00:00:22,560
>> After I did this, I got my first sale in minutes.

7
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:27,519
In just 7 months, he went from nothing to a $14,000 per month app.

8
00:00:27,519 --> 00:00:28,880
And he's just getting started.

9
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:33,200
I brought Dennis onto the channel to break down exactly how he did this.

10
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:42,160
And in this video, we'll dive into how he built his MVP in just one weekend, his exact Reddit launch strategy that got him sales in minutes,

11
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:48,239
